                    {
                        "clusion": "I",
                        "lang": "fr",
                        "value": "Pour les cas : patient, homme et femme \u00e2g\u00e9s de 0 \u00e0 79 ans inclus, ayant un premier \u00e9v\u00e8nement d\u00e9my\u00e9linisant central d\u00e9clar\u00e9 par le neurologue, dont les premiers sympt\u00f4mes de l'\u00e9pisode remontent \u00e0 moins de 12 mois. Pour les t\u00e9moins :  patient, homme et femme \u00e2g\u00e9s de 0 \u00e0 79 ans, ayant consult\u00e9 un m\u00e9decin g\u00e9n\u00e9raliste."
                    },
                    {
                        "clusion": "I",
                        "lang": "en",
                        "value": "For the cases: patients, males and females aged from 0 to 79 years, having a first central demyelinating event reported by the neurologist, for which the first symptoms of the episode occurred less than 12 months ago. For the controls:  patients, males and females aged from 0 to 79 years, having consulted a general practitioner."
                    },
